org.anchoranalysis.annotation.io.assignment.generator

Class AssignmentGenerator

  • Object
    • RasterGenerator<T>
      • RasterGeneratorSelectFormat<Assignment>
        • AssignmentGenerator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Generator<Assignment>, TransformingGenerator<Assignment,Stack>, ElementWriter<Assignment>

    public class AssignmentGenerator
extends RasterGeneratorSelectFormat<Assignment>
    Outputs a raster showing an Assignment on a background.

    Specifically two tiled backgrounds appear, one left, and one right, and objects are colored on left and right panels, to indicate how they appear in the assignment.

    Author:
    Owen Feehan
